PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Tea and Biscuits
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What makes a great cup of tea?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: The perfect cup of tea requires high-quality loose leaf tea, fresh water heated to the optimal brewing temperature, and a little patience to allow the flavors to fully develop.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: How do I choose the right biscuits to pair with my tea?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Consider the flavor profiles of both the tea and biscuits. Lighter teas like green or white pair well with delicate biscuits, while robust black teas can hold their own against richer, more indulgent biscuit varieties.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: What are some popular tea and biscuit pairings?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Classic pairings include Earl Grey with shortbread, English Breakfast with digestive biscuits, and fruity herbal teas with butter cookies or biscotti. Don't be afraid to experiment and find your own favorite combinations!
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is it okay to dunk biscuits in my tea?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Absolutely! Dunking biscuits in tea is a time-honored tradition enjoyed by many. Just be mindful not to leave them in too long, or they may become soggy and fall apart.

FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our delightful tea and biscuit offerings
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What types of tea do you offer?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: We have a wide selection of premium loose leaf teas, including black teas, green teas, herbal infusions, and seasonal blends. Our teas are sourced from the finest tea gardens around the world.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: What kinds of biscuits are available?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Our biscuit selection includes classic butter cookies, shortbread, gingerbread, biscotti, and more. We also offer gluten-free and vegan options to accommodate dietary restrictions.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I purchase tea and biscuits for gifting?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Absolutely! We have beautiful gift sets and baskets available, perfect for any occasion. Our packaging makes for an elegant and thoughtful present.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Do you offer any tea accessories?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, we carry a range of high-quality tea accessories like teapots, infusers, strainers, and more. These make wonderful additions to elevate your tea-drinking experience.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How should I store my tea and biscuits?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: For optimal freshness, store your loose leaf teas in an airtight container away from moisture, heat, and direct sunlight. Biscuits should be kept in an airtight container at room temperature.
